  "title": "Operations Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope:<br /><br /></p><p>Communicating with shipping lines, customers, and other company offices.</p><p>Coordinating and scheduling the shipment of bulk liquid products with vessel operators.</p><p>Placing bookings and issuing import/export instructions for tank containers with shipping lines, as well as collecting and forwarding all relevant documentation.</p><p>Invoicing customers and accurately allocating costs within the in-house system.</p><p>Reporting to the Senior Operator and Country Manager, supporting both internal and external requests and follow-up actions.</p><p>Building strong working relationships with vendors and communicating effectively with agents, depots, and hauliers.</p><p>Updating and maintaining shipment details in the in-house system.</p><p>Preparing Bills of Lading and other shipping documents, ensuring accuracy and timely completion.</p><p>Creating and updating quotations in the in-house system.</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:<br />Good in communication.</p><p>Candidate with atleast 2 years logistics experience.<br /></p><p><br /><strong></strong></p>",
